      <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted">Effective Date: <strong>DD Month, YYYY</strong></p>
    
      <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Your Brand Name</strong> (“we,” “our,” or “us”). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform.</p>
    
      <hr>
    
      <h3>1. Scope</h3>
      <p>This policy applies to all users including guests, hosts, and visitors browsing our platform.</p>
    
      <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
      <h5 class="mt-3">2.1 Information You Provide</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>Account details: name, email, phone, address, etc.</li>
        <li>Listings: property details, pricing, availability.</li>
        <li>Identity verification: documents like ID or selfie.</li>
        <li>Payment info (via secure third-party processors).</li>
        <li>Messages, reviews, and support interactions.</li>
      </ul>
    
      <h5 class="mt-3">2.2 Automatically Collected Info</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>Usage data: searches, clicks, bookings.</li>
        <li>Device info: IP, browser, OS, crash logs.</li>
        <li>Location: IP-based or with consent via device.</li>
      </ul>
    
      <h5 class="mt-3">2.3 From Third Parties</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>Payment/identity verification services.</li>
        <li>Marketing or analytics partners.</li>
      </ul>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">3. How We Use Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Enable and manage bookings and accounts.</li>
        <li>Verify identity and prevent fraud.</li>
        <li>Send alerts, emails, and updates.</li>
        <li>Conduct research and improve the platform.</li>
        <li>Market our services (with opt-in consent).</li>
      </ul>
    
