      <ul>
        <li>Between hosts and guests (limited info).</li>
        <li>With third-party service providers.</li>
        <li>For legal or regulatory reasons.</li>
        <li>In case of business transfers.</li>
      </ul>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">6. Cookies & Tracking</h3>
      <p>We use cookies for session management, preferences, analytics, and advertising. You can manage these in your browser settings.</p>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">7. Data Retention</h3>
      <p>We retain data as long as necessary for business and legal purposes.</p>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">8. Security</h3>
      <p>We use appropriate technical and organizational safeguards to protect your information, though no method is 100% secure.</p>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">9. International Transfers</h3>
      <p>Your data may be transferred and processed in countries with different data laws. Protections like Standard Contractual Clauses may apply.</p>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">10. Your Rights</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
        <li>Request data portability.</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with your authority.</li>
      </ul>
    
      <h3 class="mt-4">11. Children’s Privacy</h3>
